SUPERSTORE SALES ANALYTICS DASHBOARD PROJECT

Problem Statement:
The objective of this project is to analyze retail sales data to identify trends,
profitability drivers, regional performance and customer behavior.

Tools Used:
- SQL (Data querying & aggregation)
- Excel (Initial analysis)
- Power BI (Interactive dashboard & KPIs)

Key KPIs:
- Total Sales
- Total Profit
- Profit Margin %
- Average Order Value
- YTD Sales & Profit
- YoY Growth %
- Monthly Growth %

Dashboard Features:
- Regional Sales Analysis
- Category Performance Breakdown
- Monthly Sales & Profit Trends
- Decomposition Tree Analysis
- Interactive Slicers

Developed by: Anuj
Year: 2026
